---
title: Indian Chickpea & Asparagus Curry with Garlic Rice & Crushed Peanuts
description: Enjoy a bowl of creamy and rich Indian curry, loaded with colourful veggies and aromatic spices. With a sprinkling of crushed peanuts to finish it all off, this delicious meal is sure to beat your local takeaway joint!

*We’ve replaced the baby broccoli in this recipe with asparagus due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
